ch.cern.dod.db.entity

Class DODCommandParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.cern.dod.db.entity.DODCommandParam

  • public class DODCommandParam
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a parameter job that has to be carried out on a database. In the parameters we include things like the timestamp for a recovery, the config file to upload, etc.
    Author:
    Daniel Gomez Blanco
